  ../1496-2e3f23cf/skills/review-library-update-request/SKILL.md:60:   - Compare the top-level dynamic-access percentage/ratio. Do not require covered call counts or total call counts to match, and do not block just because one version has fewer dynamic-access calls.
  ../1496-2e3f23cf/skills/review-library-update-request/SKILL.md:61:   - A lower coverage percentage for the requested version is blocking unless the PR gives a concrete explanation, such as upstream removal of reachable dynamic-access sites or an intentionally narrower supported surface.
